Built on Apple's MLX (mlx.core / mlx.nn). The tokenizer and image-preprocessing
I/O boundary uses HuggingFace transformers / tokenizers and Pillow.

The DFlash and hybrid decoding paths can optionally use the external
block-diffusion drafter z-lab/Qwen3.6-27B-DFlash; those weights are downloaded
separately and are not redistributed here.
